job.title: NHDC Young Professional Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 12  Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies:12

Name of the post:

  • Young Professional, Consultant, Sr. Consultant

Description:

The National Handloom Development Corporation Limited (NHDC)  issued a total of 12 vacancies for the posts of Young Professional, Consultant, Sr. Consultant. The online application for these posts under NHDC shall start from 02.04.2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before  20.04.2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for NHDC Young Professional Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 02.04.2021
  • The Last date to apply online is  20.04.2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have the diploma/degree in LLB, CA, ICWA, MBA/PGDM, PG  to apply for the post of Young Professional, Consultant, Sr. Consultant 

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 18 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 35 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Young Professional, Consultant, Sr. Consultant is:

  • Young Professional – Rs.50,000/-
  • Consultant- Rs.80,000/-
  • Sr. Consultant- Rs.1,25,000/-

Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that NHDC issued this notification for which posts.

  •  Young Professional
  • Consultant
  • Sr. Consultant

How to apply for NHDC Young Professional Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of NHDC.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Young Professional, Consultant, Sr. Consultant.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
